    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>cooked aubergine slices</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> in a single layer</p><p>Spoon over <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> and repeat so there are two layers of aubergine and sauce</p><p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>grated</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until the cheese has browned – this is your <strong>aubergine parmigiana</strong></p>",
