    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice each <strong>ciabatta</strong> into 4 slices and place onto a baking tray (or two!) </p><p>Spread the<strong> basil pesto</strong> evenly over the <strong>ciabatta slices</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 5 min until the ciabatta is warmed through and crispy – this is your <strong>pesto bruschetta</strong></p>",
