      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>aubergine parmigiana</strong> has cooked, allow it to cool slightly before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the<strong> aubergine</strong> <strong>parmigiana</strong> with the <strong>pesto</strong> <strong>bruschetta</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
